STATE of North Carolina
v.
Restoney ROBINSON. No. 129P05-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 19, 2006. Restoney Robinson, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 12th day of April 2006 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Rowan County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 19th day of April 2006."
